title_full:
DJ Nigga Fox

              —
              Cartas Na Manga
            
              (Príncipe)
label: Príncipe
description:
DJ Nigga Fox’s most substantial release to date sets a new benchmark for Lisbon’s revered underground ghetto dance scene, pulling traces of jazz, acid house and cinematic sound design into his deeply rugged and exceptional sound with effortless style...🔥🔥🔥

Highlighted as one to watch in Lisbon’s virulent club scenius since appearing on the ‘Bazzerk’... more

Totally raw and hypnotic dub-noise brilliance plus bare-bones tresillo patterns from Portugal’s guess-again trio; Niagara

Leading on from a strong 2018 in which Alberto Arruda, António Arruda, and Sara Eckerson turned out a rugged debut LP for Príncipe and dropped two CDr’s on their Ascender label, they now home in on two contrasting sides of their aesthetic... more

release: Carregando A Vida Atrás Das Costas
title_full:
Puto Tito

              —
              Carregando A Vida Atrás Das Costas
            
              (Príncipe)
label: Príncipe
description: Insanely fresh, killer debut volley by 19 year old “veteran” of Lisbon’s virulent ghetto sound, recorded when he was just 14 and now remastered and released by the mighty Príncipe. It's a brilliantly weirdo, avant-garde fusion of portugese/angolan dance music styles championing an ideal of dance music as punkish & direct rather than overworked and generic... more
